description: This file defines the interface for the SSP implementation of the BBHM Vendor Service Provider related to web Access Control Management (ACM). It includes function prototypes for initialization and credential retrieval, and contains licensing and documentation comments.

methods.name: ssp_BbhmInitWebAcmIf
methods.description: Initializes the Web ACM Interface for BBHM.

methods.name: ssp_BbhmWebAcmIfGetCredential
methods.description: Retrieves the credential based on hostname, port, URI, username, and realm.
